{"tid":1257226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警犬】福士出警犬專用車 有冷氣有監測免不適","createTime":"2019-06-25T12:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T12:44:16.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"327b3849f76627eb91f74e98f1b56185fdef885a","tid":1257226,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190624/large/1561366531_a845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190624%2Flarge%2F1561366531_a845.jpg&h=85ca9f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n專為警犬而設，出勤無壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190624/large/1561366534_0def.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190624%2Flarge%2F1561366534_0def.jpg&h=3c7de9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後座空間夠大，避免警犬太緊張出現情緒問題。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n警犬絕對服從指令，主人指點，即時撲擊咬人，非常忠心。但警犬始終係狗狗，如果被困室內，又照顧得不好，隨時有情緒問題，不適要送院診治。所以福士(Volkswagen)就改裝旗下Caddy車款，將後座變成警犬安樂窩，出勤可以更舒適，收隊又可以攤唞一下，香港警察都可以考慮引入吖，一定實用過水炮車，而且警察們都想警犬同事出勤開心啲嘛。<br />\n<br />\n福士新設計警犬車加入戰團，就是想分Ford Transit Connect一杯羮。雖然這部Caddy van外表看來沒有特別，但尾櫳其實經過特別設計，首先加了一個有鎖的籠，而且還有足夠空間及通風系統讓警犬安全出勤。而且尾櫳亦有獨立冷氣以及溫度監測功能，遇有溫度太高或太低都會提醒駕駛者，而駕駛者亦不用下車，就可以調校尾櫳的溫度。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，性能上就是一部普通Caddy，採用2公升柴油引擎，最大馬力148hp，配上六前速自動波箱。極速可以去到190km/h，而且耗油量5l/100km，在性能及慳油中取得平衡。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：Michael<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190625/59752183?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190625%2F59752183%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDoD442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=84a66e7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190625%2F59752183%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=df9ec18a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20190625/59752183?utm_campaign=hkad_social_gadgetguy.appleseed&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5bdb58c80296b00e502c635903bfb6d79aadbf3e","tid":1257226,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"香港警察都可以考慮引入吖，一定實用過水炮車，而且警察們都想警犬同事出勤開心啲嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148a81818a22a9ced5ac7b0d99737734a681050e","tid":1257226,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bdb58c80296b00e502c635903bfb6d79aadbf3e","tid":1257226,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"香港警察都可以考慮引入吖，一定實用過水炮車，而且警察們都想警犬同事出勤開心啲嘛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8fFf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8fFf9.jpg&h=c6019c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKRASFu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKRASFu.png&h=eac30445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【警民大和解】警方高層不代表前線 市民應支持前線警員!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251511\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b